{"tid":2378793,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"挑剔魔迷：B費專殺弱旅，數據超強！","createTime":"2021-01-24T18:54:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T00:25:30.000Z","uid":154406,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"62842ff7652cd392cd144834fdff8c003834a29d","tid":2378793,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T18:54:10.000Z","msg":"紅魔中場般奴費南迪斯（B費）雖在作客紅軍一仗未有突出表現，被球迷斥責對陣Big 6球隊「冇料到」，但另一方面又凸顯B費專殺弱旅的能力，其入球和助攻次數在對陣Big 6以外的球隊相當不俗。<br />\n<br />\nB費雖然貢獻良多，但有球迷翻出這位葡萄牙中場對陣Big 6球隊的疲弱數據，批評他在雙紅會中表現沉寂，錯失良機未能為曼聯全取三分，有球迷在社交媒體斥責：「不要拿B費和奇雲迪布尼相比，他在大賽沒有表現」、「夏維斯對陣Big 6時，也比他有更多入球貢獻。」"},{"pid":"1ba75349c9418df929022db88776b77e97e8c564","tid":2378793,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T18:55:43.000Z","msg":"ching好開心？"},{"pid":"964fd2badce6598fc68a3ce59b31fa1357b9d724","tid":2378793,"uid":154406,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"1ba75349c9418df929022db88776b77e97e8c564","tid":2378793,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T18:55:43.000Z","msg":"ching好開心？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T18:56:09.000Z","msg":"同輸波嘅感覺唔同"},{"pid":"c01be247a0808e64c3a190e6fa995352048dd60e","tid":2378793,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"964fd2badce6598fc68a3ce59b31fa1357b9d724","tid":2378793,"uid":154406,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"1ba75349c9418df929022db88776b77e97e8c564","tid":2378793,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T18:55:43.000Z","msg":"ching好開心？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T18:56:09.000Z","msg":"同輸波嘅感覺唔同"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T18:56:33.000Z","msg":"唔知輸波咩感覺"},{"pid":"ba263ecf7476ce59be293c7f3e29569f7f8c6611","tid":2378793,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c01be247a0808e64c3a190e6fa995352048dd60e","tid":2378793,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"964fd2badce6598fc68a3ce59b31fa1357b9d724","tid":2378793,"uid":154406